317
00:21:33,540 --> 00:21:35,180
sometimes.

318
00:21:39,830 --> 00:21:40,940
I don't know

319
00:21:41,180 --> 00:21:42,700
what happened to him.

320
00:21:43,100 --> 00:21:45,220
Lately, he couldn't eat

321
00:21:45,580 --> 00:21:46,980
or sleep.

322
00:21:47,980 --> 00:21:49,020
And there are signs

323
00:21:49,780 --> 00:21:51,380
of recurrence of his eye disease.

324
00:21:55,660 --> 00:21:56,500
Then...

325
00:21:57,980 --> 00:21:58,940
Is it serious?

326
00:22:01,140 --> 00:22:02,340
Not so serious right now,

327
00:22:03,260 --> 00:22:04,500
but I'm not sure

328
00:22:05,220 --> 00:22:06,500
whether it'll get worse.

329
00:22:08,260 --> 00:22:09,140
Lan Che.

330
00:22:09,900 --> 00:22:10,740
Why don't you

331
00:22:12,140 --> 00:22:13,820
check on him?

332
00:22:17,820 --> 00:22:18,660
Fine.

333
00:22:20,220 --> 00:22:21,260
Lan Che.

334
00:22:22,860 --> 00:22:23,940
If you're still angry,

335
00:22:24,260 --> 00:22:25,100
you can always

336
00:22:25,260 --> 00:22:26,100
