337
00:22:26,500 --> 00:22:28,820
and make it obedient.

338
00:22:37,300 --> 00:22:39,100
Hey. Get the donkey out of here.

339
00:22:39,100 --> 00:22:41,420
(Prince's Mansion)

340
00:22:46,540 --> 00:22:49,060
(Resilient as Pine, Elegant as Bamboo)

341
00:23:05,220 --> 00:23:06,100
Why are you here?

342
00:23:06,940 --> 00:23:08,740
Feng said you had a recurrence.

343
00:23:09,540 --> 00:23:10,500
I need to check on you.

344
00:23:12,220 --> 00:23:13,180
My eyes

345
00:23:13,580 --> 00:23:14,420
