346
00:23:19,660 --> 00:23:20,940
Anyway, here's the medicine.

347
00:23:21,420 --> 00:23:23,380
Remember to take it.

348
00:23:25,380 --> 00:23:26,220
Thanks.

349
00:23:29,260 --> 00:23:31,140
